document_data.mainbody:
Caldwell Street was a dirt and gravel paved minor avenue in the Sea Ward of Waterdeep.
Caldwell stretched from north to south, with the northern end terminating on Gulzindar Street and the southern end terminating on Julthoon Street.In the map included in the 1-edition accessory City System, this locations name was misprinted as "Gulzinder Street".
